{"tid":2210151,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"做人有太多夢想 好事定壞事","createTime":"2020-09-20T07:54:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-20T07:56:14.000Z","uid":207360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b0e98254e0f2520ad303aef79d537f211fc33e44","tid":2210151,"uid":207360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T07:54:47.000Z","msg":"究竟太多夢想係好事家壞事。<br />\n中學讀書對工程有興趣但冇讀，就去大學讀左濕9科目...<br />\n見到身邊朋友讀左專科因為覺得好羨慕又自己去左讀(非工程）讀完先發覺而家呢個時世好難搵工<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n身邊又有朋友返緊工而家讀緊part-time 測量Asso，講到好好境咁，搞到我又心郁郁... 但點都好好一定要返工搵左筆錢先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n究竟做人有好多唔同既多夢係因為堅定/搖擺不定<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8ef69bfe5f927c1cdd3a54fe497deaf7fd69ea0","tid":2210151,"uid":82955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T07:56:14.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"pink\">【錄埋出嚟Diu多次】既然黃絲咁鐘意互Diu 就等我Diu哂你地所有人2</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2210104\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2210104</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mmipv76.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmmipv76.png&h=e3a7ffc0&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}